            "notes": "The key concept of this deck is to overwhelm the opponent with aggressive creatures and direct damage spells in order to quickly reduce their life total to zero. By utilizing cards like Goblin Guide, Dragon's Rage Channeler, and Blightstep Pathway, the deck aims to apply constant pressure and force the opponent to react defensively. The inclusion of powerful removal spells like Terminate and Fatal Push allows the deck to efficiently deal with any threats the opponent may play. Additionally, cards like Demonic Tutor and Tainted Pact provide the deck with consistent card advantage and flexibility to find the necessary cards to secure victory. Ultimately, this deck looks to outpace and outmaneuver the opponent in order to emerge victorious in a one-on-one duel."
