            "notes": "The deck focuses on utilizing a wide variety of artifacts to ramp quickly and control the board while dealing damage to the opponent efficiently. The key strategy is to flood the battlefield with cheap artifacts to power up The Fantasticar and overwhelm the opponent with a mix of aggression and disruption. By combining artifact acceleration with disruptive tools like Pithing Needle and Tormod's Crypt, the deck aims to control the game and dictate the pace of play. With a mix of mana rocks, utility artifacts, and controlling pieces, the deck synergizes around a central theme of artifact-based aggression, aiming to disrupt the opponent's plans while beating them down with a swarm of powerful artifacts."
